45
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:13,560
The wedding robe will be the first.

46
00:04:14,430 --> 00:04:15,630
You always know how to tease me!

47
00:04:16,070 --> 00:04:17,560
The measuring tools are in the study.

48
00:04:17,750 --> 00:04:18,590
I'll go get them.

49
00:04:18,630 --> 00:04:19,750
Let's talk in the study, then.

50
00:04:22,530 --> 00:04:27,010
