♪Let them end with a final grace♪

52
00:04:29,410 --> 00:04:33,810
♪Burn away my memories of snow♪

53
00:04:33,810 --> 00:04:36,330
♪And the deceit♪

54
00:04:36,330 --> 00:04:40,650
♪Let me cherish one last look♪

55
00:04:40,650 --> 00:04:43,000
♪In your gentle gaze♪

56
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:46,370
♪Our last kiss is so tender♪

57
00:04:46,370 --> 00:04:49,960
♪In the next life, may we never meet♪

58
00:04:51,510 --> 00:04:52,350
Wait for me a moment.

59
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:07,650
♪Rain slips through my fingers♪

60
00:05:07,650 --> 00:05:09,620
♪Falling into the abyss♪

61
00:05:11,610 --> 00:05:14,440
♪Fates entwine♪

62
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:16,780
♪Weaving a tale of parting♪

63
00:05:17,470 --> 00:05:20,700
♪The candle flickers as I fall again♪

64
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:23,350
♪Gently holding your face closer♪

65
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,400
Yao,

66
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,830
this all feels too good to be true,

67
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:29,430
like a dream.

68
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,520
But Chen,

69
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:35,390
if it's a dream,
we must eventually wake up.

70
00:05:35,390 --> 00:05:38,080
♪Even in pain, let me draw near♪

71
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:40,470
♪Can this fleeting sweetness linger♪

72
